experience.description:
Project to organize auto watering. The cornerstone of it is Arduino Nano v. 3 microcontroller. Embedded software were written on C++. 
My responsibilities: 
1) Development of project structure; 
2) Writing source code; 
3) Testing and debugging; 
4) Refactoring of code. 
At the moment, this is the most interesting experience for me. I have used algorithms and data structures in practice and have studied the C++ syntax. I have learned how to use computer memory efficiently. 
In addition, the gained knowledge helped me to understand Python better.
